<TextSection>
  <h3 id="intelligent-investor">
    1.
    <span class="link--theme">"The Intelligent Investor"</span>
    by Benjamin Graham
  </h3>

  <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto">
    <ProductCard
      title="The Intelligent Investor"
      href="https://amzn.to/3RWaUZo"
      siteLink="https://amzn.to/3RWaUZo"
      imgLink="https://images.fineartamerica.com/images/artworkimages/mediumlarge/3/the-intelligent-investor-benjamin-graham-investment-classics-edward-g.jpg"
    />
  </div>

  <h3 class="!mt-6 link--theme">Summary:</h3>
  <p>
    <span class="link--theme">"The Intelligent Investor"</span> by Benjamin Graham
    is a timeless classic on value investing that emphasizes long-term financial
    success through careful analysis, risk management, and discipline in the world
    of stocks and bonds. It offers invaluable insights for investors seeking a rational
    and systematic approach to achieving their financial goals.
  </p>

  <h3 class="link--theme">What It Teaches:</h3>
  <p>
    <span class="link--theme">"The Intelligent Investor"</span> teaches readers the
    principles of value investing, advocating for a patient, disciplined, and analytical
    approach to stock market investing. It emphasizes the importance of margin of
    safety and understanding intrinsic value to make informed, long-term investment
    decisions.
  </p>

  <h3 class="link--theme">Amazon Review:</h3>
  <p class="text-sm">
    "This book is perhaps the most important and insightful book on investing,
    and an eternal classic."
  </p>

  <p>
    Buy <a
      target="_blank"
      class="underline link--theme"
      href="https://amzn.to/3RWaUZo">"The Intelligent Investor"</a
    >
  </p> On Amazon
</TextSection>

