  <p>
    "The Art of War" by Sun Tzu is an ancient Chinese military treatise that
    offers timeless wisdom on strategy, leadership, and tactics. It explores
    principles of warfare that have been applied to various aspects of life,
    including business and personal development.
  </p>

  <h3 class="link--theme">What It Teaches:</h3>
  <p>
    "The Art of War" teaches readers the importance of strategic thinking,
